{"tid":857680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海砂價錢十年貴一倍 向支那買砂為「明日大嶼」料花$439億 (未計超支)","createTime":"2018-10-11T09:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T10:21:35.000Z","uid":176442,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f30b09163388270c402044908c231f3883ac1b33","tid":857680,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb4b7cd135b51f1ee51a94cdf3e77ddf0daa4b3","tid":857680,"uid":156363,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvRcPjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnvRcPjg.jpg&h=bbe8dd52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又話中央幾關照香港？？搵幾隻呢D南海人工島既自煮燃發造陸船一年就造到個島出黎啦，隻船識自己採沙同時係船頭噴沙。"},{"pid":"3148752d41ddc868ff94142955daea0845f5a99d","tid":857680,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"買砂都500億 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係移山填海咩"},{"pid":"53db06a2ed229c13081a1b66dc9025bd1defbb6a","tid":857680,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6de1a938596de6a1c614cd9777d4166deb24218","tid":857680,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"呢啲好有利益輸送feel"},{"pid":"80f1b0dc4b2bbb9c832575e427f82f0c56f0f42b","tid":857680,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170730000905-260412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170730000905-260412&d=pWbpC%2BUQwT7NA%2FgVgW1ez9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9b4d5c16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170730000905-260412</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KW2O68q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKW2O68q.jpg&h=029a0de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天鯨號 大陸造島神器禁止出口<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國大陸在南海造島，僅僅只花18個月，就修築了近3000英畝（約合12.14平方公里）陸地</strong>，主要是靠挖泥船「天鯨號」挖掘、排泥能力。<br />\n<br />\n在7月23日派記者登上「天鯨號」參訪，腳踩上「天鯨號」甲板，並不會有「上船」的感覺，而更像是身處一個建築工地&mdash;&mdash;四周和頭頂都是鋼架和吊臂。只不過，這個「建築工地」非常乾淨，沒有塵土飛揚。由於「天鯨號」因有「建築工地」屬性，參觀者被要求只要走出船艙，就必須戴上安全帽。<br />\n<br />\n「天鯨號」被中國網民稱為「造島神器」，這個稱號來源於其強大的挖掘和吹填能力。船上工作人員指出，<strong>它每小時可挖掘4500立方米的海底混合物，這相當於可以挖出一個標準足球場大、半米深的坑。</strong><br />\n<br />\n如此強大的能力要歸功於其堅實的「拳頭」&mdash;&mdash;位於船頭位置的絞刀頭。平時從網路照片裡很難看出這個「拳頭」真正的大小，只有站在它面前才會被震撼到。<br />\n<br />\n「造島神器」還有兩個「殺手鐧」--強大的自航能力和先進的自動挖泥控制系統。位於挖泥船頂層的駕駛艙是實現這兩大功能的「大腦」。駕駛艙內高科技感十足，令人聯想到科幻電影中的太空船駕駛艙。自動挖泥控制系統位於艙內正中，所有挖泥設備的操作集成在約兩平方米的操作台上，點擊游標或按鈕便可完成設備的遠程操作。工作人員表示，船員甚至可以一邊挖泥，一邊悠閒地喝杯茶。<br />\n<br />\n大陸商務部和海關總署宣布對大型工程船舶實施出口管制。其中絞刀功率大於或等於500千瓦，挖深大於或等於15米，總裝機功率大於或等於2000千瓦的絞吸式挖泥船，未經許可一律不得出口。「天鯨號」所屬的天航局表示「我們的船可以到世界其他國家施工，但如果其他國家想買，是不可能的」。"},{"pid":"d1b0f0bdae254a083269136373ef22809b760aee","tid":857680,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"156091bc4e1acbca72039b7549c8919add47024a","tid":857680,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1b0f0bdae254a083269136373ef22809b760aee","tid":857680,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"2097c098d670aacb3710500b8c0bb42a6cba9329","tid":857680,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1b0f0bdae254a083269136373ef22809b760aee","tid":857680,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:55:43.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n習近平都係旨在打個和，大家開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e589d9f4e4e0232e4e9b041c901d5c9f86624177","tid":857680,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"直接買起大灣區既地.會唔會平D."},{"pid":"216e81346dc16e910681f3e6ef7812a367e05c47","tid":857680,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"用400買沙不如用100收新界地"},{"pid":"5792683d801cf998527f76d578f5d978609740be","tid":857680,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d1b0f0bdae254a083269136373ef22809b760aee","tid":857680,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"根本填海既砂係平到嘔，賣俾香港先吊高個價咋，不過香港人又肯BUY姐。"},{"pid":"a82bac8abcc097aa2fc3a9021f4ca6f9deee4c19","tid":857680,"uid":46267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:21:35.000Z","msg":"加密作用係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}